            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "The stargut hydra lurches its entire body, spewing forth chunks of meteorite in a 30-foot cone that deal 5d6 bludgeoning damage to all creatures in the area (basic Reflex DC 25). The area becomes difficult terrain for 1 minute, though a creature can use an Interact action to clear one square of the rubble. The stargut hydra can't Vomit Meteorites for 1d4 rounds.",
